@startuml UEORMS_Sequence_13
!pragma teoz true
autonumber
hide footbox

control "Express API Layer\n(app.js route orchestration)" as API
control "Notification Service" as Notify
control "Email Service + Queue" as Email
control "Billing Service" as Billing
entity "Stripe / Razorpay" as Gateway
database "PostgreSQL via Prisma" as DB

== 13) Subscription Webhooks and External Billing ==
Gateway -> API : POST /api/billing/webhooks/stripe|razorpay
API -> Billing : validate signature/event + idempotency check
Billing -> DB : BillingEvent find/create/update
alt event not processed
  Billing -> DB : update subscription/payment state
  Billing -> Notify : subscription/billing notification
  Billing -> Email : invoice email / failure notice
else already processed
  Billing --> API : idempotent ack
end
API --> Gateway : webhook acknowledged


@enduml